  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c513d81420ae4244ea5fa86c11a4a29b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Start_Dialog
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogData
  characterName: Jack
  lines:
  - Thank goodness you're here. We're swamped for work right now.
  - We've developed an AI module that could potentially automate a lot of our workload,
    but we need a small robot to install it in for testing.
  - Could you build one for us? In return I can tell you about Artificial Intelligence!
